name: IKEA ALGOT System Planner
description:
Drawn to scale so you can test different configurations of the IKEA Algot Wall System. Just drag the parts you want like shelves, rails and baskets onto the uprights to create your perfect system.

The uprights include markings so you can see how many spaces a particular configuration takes up. Use these markings to how much space you need between shelves etc.

Included are:

- Uprights
- Shelves
- Rails
- Baskets
- Spacer
- Labels (Click inside the shelf, rail or basket to hide and show)

If you have any suggestions or requests feel free to contact me.
